snippet.title: Returner Zhero Early Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Returner Zhero - A space mystery puzzle game coming soon to iOS

The first peek of the new game from Fantastic, yes game studios. The content in this video is still a work in progress, and may not fully reflect the final game.
